    <item>
      <title>美联储将下调利率路径预测：太平洋投资管理公司（Pimco）总裁威尔丁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-13/fed-will-revise-down-rate-path-estimates-pimco-s-wilding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pimco 经济学家蒂芙尼·怀尔丁表示，美国经济并未陷入衰退，美联储应专注于将政策利率恢复到中性水平。她在“彭博监测”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-13/fed-will-revise-down-rate-path-estimates-pimco-s-wilding</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 13:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉维持南非改革期间信用展望稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/fitch-keeps-south-africa-s-credit-outlook-stable-amid-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级维持南非债务的稳定展望，理由是南非经济改革略有改善，债务增长放缓，避免了南非信用评级进一步下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/fitch-keeps-south-africa-s-credit-outlook-stable-amid-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 13:16:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Avolon 将收购 Castlelake 的飞机租赁部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/avolon-to-buy-castlelake-s-aircraft-leasing-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Avolon Holdings 同意以未公开的金额收购 Castlelake LP 的飞机租赁部门，这笔交易将为这家爱尔兰租赁公司的投资组合增加 118 架喷气式飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/avolon-to-buy-castlelake-s-aircraft-leasing-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 12:53:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷增长疲弱，中国人民银行暗示将帮助经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-s-credit-growth-slowed-in-august-as-confidence-stays-weak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信贷数据显示，尽管此前多次降息，但私人信心依然疲弱，中国央行表示将加大抗击通货紧缩的力度，并准备出台更多政策来重振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-s-credit-growth-slowed-in-august-as-confidence-stays-weak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 11:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国最终确定拜登 5 月宣布提高对华关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/us-trade-agency-finalizes-china-tariffs-biden-announced-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的政府周五正式批准对价值数十亿美元的中国商品提高关税，为大部分关税在两周内生效铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/us-trade-agency-finalizes-china-tariffs-biden-announced-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 11:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德暗示欧洲央行可能在 10 月降息，但 12 月更有可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，如果经济遭遇重大挫折，欧洲央行愿意在 10 月份考虑降息——不过下一轮全面信息要到下次会议上才能公布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因恒大欺诈行为对普华永道处以创纪录罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-fines-pwc-halts-business-for-six-months-over-evergrande</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国因普华永道会计师事务所对中国恒大集团的审计存在疏漏，暂停了该事务所的运营六个月，并对其处以创纪录的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-fines-pwc-halts-business-for-six-months-over-evergrande</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员预计美联储下周降息半个百分点的可能性为 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/treasuries-gain-as-traders-weigh-large-fed-rate-cut-possibility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员将美联储周五大幅降息的可能性提升至 40%，这推动了美国国债的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/treasuries-gain-as-traders-weigh-large-fed-rate-cut-possibility</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 02:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
